      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMRON TOY (1) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (37.75) from Box 1 at Bendigo over 660m. Boasts three wins from four starts out of this box. Worth another chance. FLEEING (7) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 1.4 lengths (33.99) at Sandown. Should be in this for a long way. IN BLOOM (8) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at her last five runs. Last start finished 3rd over 730m at this track beaten 6 lengths (43.46) behind Mepunga Breeze in a Grade 4/5 on June 20. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Deserves a win and gets her chance. SHIMA BLUSH (5) will need to run right up to last start to feature again.",
